Why sometime it take few seconds to launch an app? Swiftly switch can\'t start apps within 5 seconds from the point you return the Home Screen. This is the how Android limit services. It\'s not a problem if you return home by the in app Home Shortcut, or even better - do not return to the Home Screen.
